&quot;Another World&quot; is the second studio album delivered by Queen guitarist Brian May.

Tracklist:

01.&quot;Space&quot; - 0:47
02.&quot;Business&quot; - 5:07
03.&quot;China Belle&quot; - 4:01
04.&quot;Why Don't We Try Again&quot; - 5:24
